data.description: A fabulous opportunity awaits on Phillips Dr! Over 3000 sq.ft. to make your own. Solid brick home with awesome covered patios in front and back. Three separate living areas offer many options. The garage has been converted into a cozy family room with wood burning stove, bathroom and built in cabinetry. The spacious kitchen has nice wood floors, some newer appliances, updated countertops and is ready for some good cooking! Tuff Shed measures approximately 10' X 12'. Seasonal plantings are vibrant and provide nice privacy and curb appeal. Both front entrances have wheelchair accessible ramps. Partial upgrades in bathrooms. Large .22-acre lot offers plenty of space for parking and backyard fun! Centrally located, close to everything in beautiful Las Cruces. This has been a great family home over the years. Make it your place today! PRICED BELOW RECENT APPRAISAL.
